This place is a new neighborhood gem. They have a wide selection of delicious Italian cheeses, antipasti, as well as cold and hot dishes. They also have a wide variety of cold cuts and make great sandwiches for customers on the go. Borgo Italia isn't just a deli, it's also a small market with plenty of Italian pastas, olive oils, spices and herbs, and beverages. It's so clean and organized!! Perfect place to go for a quick lunch or to stock up on quality Italian goods. Added bonus - they do gourmet catering for small groups and occasions!
